"select queries. To do this under Unix:"
msgstr ""
"pgsql2shp je alat komandne linije za izvoz PostgreSQL tabela, pogleda ili "
"SQL select upita. Za to na Uniksu:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:51
msgid "To export the data using a query:"
msgstr "Za izvoz podataka pomoću upita:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:59
msgid "ogr2ogr"
msgstr "ogr2ogr"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:61
msgid ""
"ogr2ogr is a very powerful tool to convert data into and from PostgreSQL to "
"many data formats. ogr2ogr is part of the GDAL library and has to be "
"installed separately. To export a table from PostgreSQL to GML, you can use "
"this command:"
msgstr ""
"ogr2ogr je veoma moćan alat za pretvaranje podataka u PostgreSQL i iz njega "
"u mnoge formate podataka. ogr2ogr je deo GDAL biblioteke i mora se "
"instalirati zasebno. Za izvoz tabele iz PostgreSQL-a u GML, možete koristiti"
" ovu komandu:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:71
msgid "DB Manager"
msgstr "DB Manager"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:73
msgid ""
"You may have noticed another option in the :guilabel:`Database` menu labeled"
" :guilabel:`DB Manager`. This is a tool that provides a unified interface "
"for interacting with spatial databases including PostgreSQL. It also allows "
"you to import and export from databases to other formats. Since the next "
"module is largely devoted to using this tool, we will only briefly mention "
"it here."
msgstr ""
"Možda ste primetili još jednu opciju u meniju :guilabel:`Baza podataka` pod "
"nazivom :guilabel:`DB menadžer`. To je alat koji pruža jedinstven interfejs "
"za rad sa prostornim bazama podataka, uključujući PostgreSQL. Takođe vam "
"omogućava uvoz i izvoz iz baza podataka u druge formate. Pošto je sledeći "
"modul u velikoj meri posvećen korišćenju ovog alata, ovde ćemo ga samo "
"ukratko pomenuti."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:82
msgid "In Conclusion"
msgstr "Zaključak"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:84
msgid ""
"Importing and exporting data to and from the database can be done in many "
"various ways. Especially when using disparate data sources, you will "
"probably use these functions (or others like them) on a regular basis."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz i izvoz podataka u bazu podataka i iz nje može se obaviti na mnogo "
"različitih načina. Naročito pri korišćenju različitih izvora podataka, "
"verovatno ćete ove funkcije (ili druge slične njima) koristiti redovno."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:89
msgid "What's Next?"
msgstr "Šta je sledeće?"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/spatial_databases/import_export.rst:91
msgid "Next we'll look at how to query the data we've created before."
msgstr ""
"Zatim ćemo pogledati kako da postavljamo upite nad podacima koje smo "
"prethodno napravili."
